ReadOnlyMode: read only mode - release of charge is not send to charger (to use RFID tags)
StateHomeBatSoc: object-id for current home battery state of charge [%]
StateHomePowerConsumption: object-id for current home power consumption [W]
StateHomeSolarPower: object-id for currently available solar power [W]
SubtractSelfConsumption: Charger consumption is included in home power consumption value
polltimelive: Time between data polls from charger [ms]
